%h1 First Replacement Guardian
%p.section-text You should specify who you wish to administer your estate and carry out your wishes in your will. It s advisable to have more than one guardian but less than four. You can have professional guardians and Notary Express can act in this capacity.
%hr

= form_for [@will, @guardian] do |f|

  .field
    = question "05060"
    = f.check_box :replacement_guardian
  %div{"data-condition" => ":checked", "data-require" => "#guardian_replacement_guardian", "data-true" => "hide"}
    = f.submit 'Save', class: "button radius"

%div{"data-condition" => ":checked", "data-require" => "#guardian_replacement_guardian", "data-false" => "hide"}
  = form_for [@will, @guardian] do |f|
    = f.fields_for :first_replacement_guardian_general_detail do |builder|
      = render "general_details/general_details_form", :builder => builder, :nested_origin => @guardian.first_replacement_guardian_general_detail
    .field
      = question "05070"
      = f.check_box :replacement_second_guardian

    = f.submit 'Save', class: "button radius"